book:

Mathematical Functions
Math



 &reftitle.intro;


  These math functions will only handle values within the range of
  the int and float types.
  To handle larger numbers, take a look at the
  arbitrary precision math or
  GNU Multiple Precision functions functions.




  &reftitle.seealso;




